{"tid":1467144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又到左香港社運祖傳既捉鬼時刻","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:02.000Z","uid":121058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c9713a622b2b954e1f0475205fac1575c2c5ee","tid":1467144,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"屌 疑神疑鬼做乜撚野<br />\n你地咪撚唔記得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">次次社運叫捉鬼就係由盛轉衰既轉捩點</span></span><br />\n由個社運第一日開始 就有警犬混入嫁啦<br />\n一直唔捉鬼成個運動到依家都相安無事 幾隻鬼有撚殺傷力咩<br />\n今日成班係度捉鬼捉鬼 個個疑神疑鬼 亂哂方寸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94144f32a4b3533239377844414000cbd39dafc2","tid":1467144,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化不割蓆</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">團結就是力量</span></span>"},{"pid":"79f1d9a6a4574005117ee0c3c43f4f165b782f33","tid":1467144,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"和理非 取消黑衫行動 勇武就無左保護 鬼亦無咁多機會滲透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要支持 勇武就無左保護 自然要勇武休息下<br />\n咁鬼既滲透亦無左機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係 講到明有下場既就全民黑衫 （例如免費過海之類）<br />\n<br />\n機場只宣傳 同控制人流 有人搞事就 比泛民 等泛民開記者會<br />\n<br />\n幫手講佢係鬼 <br />\n<br />\n另外唔建議帶口罩 和理非活動係要一家大細都可以參與"},{"pid":"44d4c2bb1bda10735721ad95c6eedeb330012e49","tid":1467144,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:36.000Z","msg":"咪撚再捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8babf96232817ea94b054e5dc0fd61c9a26e51","tid":1467144,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:02.000Z","msg":"警犬一承認有鬼就陣腳大亂<br />\n又唔係第一日有鬼 <br />\n捉鬼只會令內部分裂<img 